 of Schumann\nresonances and contemporary values of capacitances, inductances and\nresistances). The theory is also applied to the control of the oscillation\namplitude of a (damped) oscillator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Oct 2013 02:10:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Sep 2014 20:01:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 26 Sep 2015 01:40:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-29"}
