^\\nu \\hspace{0.5cm} \\mbox{where }\n\\nu=\\sqrt{\\mu^2+2\\rho/g}\\:. $$\n  This confirms and extends several results obtained previously by approximate\nmethods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Oct 2013 08:06:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-02"}
