ly suppressed due to the dominating Cooper pair scattering caused by the\nintrinsic microstructure of the FEBID deposit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Oct 2013 13:08:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-25"}
